===Kansas State===
{{AFB game box start
| Title = '''Nebraska at Kansas State''' <nowiki>[box score]</nowiki> </small>
| Visitor = '''Nebraska'''
| Host = [[1994 Kansas State Wildcats football team|Kansas State]]
